  Na7 kong2 pun2-chiaN5 khoaN3 bo5 khi2 Kheng3-tong5, kau3 boe2--a2 e7 kai2-pian3 thai3-tou7, hoan7-se3-a2 to7-si7 Kheng3-tong5 kou3-ke, thiaN3-kiaN2, kap A-eng kou3 chhu3-tau e5 koan-liam7 chin hah8. Ah na7 kong2 in e7 hiah sek8, siong-ti, iau2-si7 nng7-lang5 chiap8 cho3-hoe2 e5 koan-he7. Che long2 si7 hit-te3 lam3-chhan5 kai2 chhai3-hng5-a2 in2-khi2. A-tian2 the5-gi7, beh chiang2-ak chhai3-goan5, te7 to u7--a, put-ju5 ka-ti7 cheng3-chhai3, li7-sun5 ma7 khah che7. Tan2 chhai3-kou2 khui--loh8-khi3, peng2-thou5 ia7-chi2, ti7-chhau2 loh8-pui5, ak-chui2 phu7-ioh8, ban2-chhai3 se2-chhai3... Oa5, long2 tioh8 kang, ¡§M7-chai hiah bo5-eng5,¡¨ A-tian2 ju2 cho3 ju2 sian7, siuN7 beh kiu-kha. A-eng khoaN3-khoaN3 m7-si7 pan7-hoat, thau5-mng5 kah ah8 se2--loh8-khi3, chi2-ho2 iang Kheng3-tong5 tau3-saN-kang7. Kheng3-tong5 chin e7 kau tiang--li7, am3-thau5-a2 cheng2-li2 chhai3-hng5-a2, soa3--loh8 ban2-chhai3 se2-chhai3, thau3-cha2 sang3 lai5 chhai3-ke3-a2, kui-boe2 kui chhai3-hng5-a2 khang-khoe3 long2 i bau7--khi3. Sui-jian5 sng3-sng3--leh bo5 khah tiong5, u7 Kheng3-tong5 khang-khoe3 thaN2-tiau5--leh, eng3 chhai3-ke3-a2 e5 li7-pian7, hou7 A-eng ke chin bian2 chhau-hoan5. A-eng ma7 si5-kiaN5 hong5-hun khi3 hng5-a2 san3-pou7, sun7-soa3 khoaN3 keh thiN-kng e5 chhai3-sek.
  Chu7 se3-han3 jit8-si5 kou3-tiam3, am3-si5 thak8-chheh. Ke3 Sin-thiam liau2, bo5-eng5 teh than3-chiN5, nng7-ang-bou2 ia7 m7-bat sio-chhoa7 san3-pou7, chng-kha chhan5-hng5 keng2-sek, kau3 saN-chap8 goa7 hoe3 chiah khi3 the2-hoe7 tioh8 i sui2 e5 chit8-bin7. Tu5-liau2 chheng-hong chhoe boan2-he5, lau5-chui2 phoaN7 chiau2-siaN, hoan7-se3-a2 A-eng ai3 lau Kheng3-tong5 kong2 chit8-koa2 te7-hng e5 hong-but8, hou7 i gan2, hiN7 toa7-khui. Ki5-sit8 Kheng3-tong5 peng7 bo5 chhui3 sui2, put-si5 si7 mng7--e5 lang5 teh kong2, in3--e5 lang5 chiah chhap chit8-nng7-ku3. ChhiuN7 chit8-pai2 A-eng mng7: ¡§Li2 bat khi3 Tek8-hoa3-ke--bo5?¡¨ ¡§Bat khi3--koe3.¡¨ ¡§Si7 lan2 Tai5-oan5 lam5-pak-hoe3 e5 chong2-kin-thau5 ne,¡¨ Kong2 kah kam2-a2-tiam3-hoe3, A-eng cheng-sin5 to7 lai5: ¡§M7-na7 soaN-san2 hai2-san2, ma7 si7 chin3-khau2-hoe3 e5 toa7-poaN5.¡¨ Na2 lian5-chu-phau3, soa3--loh8-khi3 it-tit8 kong2: ¡§Goa2 chin3-cheng5 khi3, oa5! Lian5 hi5-chun5-a2 tai7-liok8-hoe3 to kui-chhu3-keng, beh tih8 siaN2 to7 u7 siaN2.¡¨ Tut8-jian5 siuN7 khi2 ho2-chhio3 e5 tai7-chi3: ¡§Ma7 u7 pou3-chhi7-ke ne. Hit-chun7 goa2 toa7-pak-tou2 phaiN7 Eng2-siong5, khoaN3-tioh8 pou3-chhi7 to7 oat jip8-khi3 lau-lau--leh, thai3 chai-iaN2 lau tiam2-goa7-cheng chhut--lai5, su-pah-lu3 phang3-kiN3--a....¡¨ ¡§Hoe3-but8-a2 to u7 lang5 thau sai2--khi3-oh?¡¨ ¡§Iau2 u7 kui-chhia e5 hoe3 ne!¡¨ A-eng thou2 chit8-e7 chih8: ¡§Tang-si5-a2 hou7 keng3-chhat thoa khi3 po2-koan2, chit-tau2 bo5 phang3-kiN3 khah ka-chai3. Tai5-pak oh theng5-chhia, kui-ki2 koh che7, i2-au7 goan2 to7 bo5-ai3 khi3--a......¡¨ A-eng siuN7 kong2 na7 chun2 beh khi3, hng7-lou7 ma7 tioh8 A-thiam sai2-chhia. SiuN7 khi2 A-thiam...., oe7 kau3 na5-au5-thau5, nge7 ka thun--loh8.
  Ki5-sit8 nng7-lang5 saN-hoe7 nng7-hoe7, lan5-bian2 e7 hoe7 tui3 in ka-ti7 ang-bou2 khi3. ¡§Sun7 kau-hoaN7 it-tit8 khi3, thang3 toa7-lou7 pian3-thau5 chui2-chhiang5 hia,¡¨ A-eng siap chhut tui3 in Sin-thiam e5 chhim-cheng5: ¡§Goan2 A-thiam kio3 goa2 ke3--i, khoaN3 i kui-bin7 ang5-ki3-ki3, kong2-tioh8 oe7 kiu-kiu-lun-lun, kiaN goa2 m7-kheng2 ne..... Goa2 thai3 e7 m7-kheng2--leh, i lang5 siong7 sit8-chai7, to7-si7 boe7-tang3 poe5 goan2 chit8-si3-lang5.....¡¨ Siong-kam2 e5 oe7 put-si5 e7 lau5--chhut-lai5. Kang7-khoan2 Kheng3-tong5 ma7 put-si5 siap chhut tui3 in A-hiong e5 su-liam7. Ti7 bo5-i3-tiong, Kheng3-tong5 thau3-lou7, i tak8-hang7 to goan5-liong7 in A-hiong, ng3-bang7 in A-hiong ma7 e7-tang3 khoan-liong7 i e5 chhong2-pong7, hoe5-sim tng2-i3, kin2 to3-tng2--lai5. Goan5-lai5 in A-hiong e7 khi3 hou7 but8 hiah thiam2, si7 chiong kui2-lo7 ni5 beh be2 chhu3 khiam7 e5 chiN5 poah8-poah8 hui2-hui2--tiau7. ¡§Na2 sin5-hun5 hou7 mou5-sin5-a2 liah8--khi3-leh, phou7-a2-te2 chap8-peh-ban7, kap nng7-khau2 oah8-hoe7 long2 pio khi3 poah8-tiau7!¡¨ Hit-chun7 e7-kang2 cho3-kang-a2-lang5 beh tiam3 Tai5-pak be2 chhu3, si7 bo5 hoat-tou7 e5 tai7-chi3. M7-koh, SaN-teng5-pou kong-u2 chiah gou7, lak8-chap8-ban7, thai3 e7 chai-iaN2 siuN7 beh khi3 koe3 teng7, phaiN2-un7 khi3 hou7 lang5 liah8 khi3 koaiN......, kui-boe2 chiN5 bo5, bou2 koh chau2--khi3. Kheng3-tong5 put-si5 oan3-than3, si7 an2-choaN2 thiN-kong-peh--a2 e7 tui3 i an2-ne. I m7-sin3 A-hiong hiah choat8-cheng5, bun7-te5 si7 A-hiong thai3 long2 bo5 phoe bo5 bun5, bo5 siau bo5 sit--leh.....
  Beng5-ki5 chu7 hit-pai2 sit-thai3, kiN3-tioh8 A-eng phaiN2-se3 phaiN2-se3. A-eng jin7-ui5 chiu2-au7 kek-khong, tong3-cho3 na2 bo5 hoat-seng--leh, lai5 hoa3-kai2 Beng5-ki5 e5 put-an. M7-koh, A-eng hong5-hun ai3 khi3 hng5-a2 lau-lau--leh, soah hou7 in Eng2-siong5 ke oe7. It-kiu2-pat-sam-ni5 chhun, Eng2-siong5 chha2 beh chham-ka Tai5-tiong-khu ko-tiong lian5-kho2. A-eng thiaN in to7-su kong2, i sit8-lek8 tai7-khai3 ti7 ji7, saN-kham2 chi3-goan7, na7 kho2 Chiang-hoa3-khu, Chiang-tiong iau2 u7 bang7. ¡§Lang5 A-gim2 to7 beh kho2 Tai5-tiong, goa2 to7 boe7-eng--tit?¡¨ Eng2-siong5 toa7-siaN khong3-gi7: ¡§I si7 iaN5 goa2 joa7 che7?¡¨ A-gim2 si7 Jit8-seng e5 oaN7-thiap-toa7, Tan5 Eng5-chin3 e5 ban-a2-kiaN2, lang5 long2 kio3 i-su-juh, Tan5 li2-su7 gou7-chap8-hoe3 seN--e5, kui-ke-hoe2-a2 sioh kah na2 mia7. M7-koh, A-eng iau2-si7 m7-kheng2, Tai5-tiong tioh8 poaN5-chhia, put pi2 Chiang-hoa3 hong-pian7. Siong7-chhiaN2 Tai5-tiong na7 kho2 boe7 tioh8 li2-siong2 hak8-hau7, put-ju5 thak8 chai7-te7. Eng2-siong5 khoaN3 in bu2--a m7-kheng2, choan2 kiu5 a-kong, a-ma2, Jit8-seng sui-jian5 thiaN3 sun, iau2-si7 chun-tiong7 in bu2--a e5 koat-teng7. chu7 an2-ne liau2, Eng2-siong5 thak8-chheh to7 pang3-sang, the3-pou7 chin che7. A-eng chit8-e7 mng7--leh, in3 kong2 to7 beh kho2 Chiang-hoa3 nia5, ah8-sai2 siuN piaN3, jia2 A-eng siong-sim koh the3 i hoan5-lo2. Chit8-jit8, chheng-beng5 koe3 liau2 jit8-thau5 u7 khah tng5, A-eng khah oaN3 chu2-am3, Eng2-siong5 boe7-hu3 chiah8 to7 beh khi3 pou2-sip8, A-eng kin2 png7 chha2 bah-si chham nng7 seng hou7 chiah8, chhui3-oan5-a2-thng to chiah leh kun2, Eng2-siong5 png7 pe bo5 kui2 chhui3: ¡§M7-si7 chheng-beng5 khi3 kui3-choa2, iah-si7 chha2 a-pa ai3 chiah8--e5...,¡¨ Sui-jian5 Eng2-siong5 kui-chhui3 png7 na2 pou7 na2 kong2, A-eng thiaN kah chin chheng-chho2. ¡§Kan-taN chiu2 tiam3 chhai3-hng5-a2..., li2 kam2 u7-iaN2 ai3 a-pa? Li2 long2 phian3--e5!¡¨ Hiong5-hiong5 oaN2-ti7 toa7-e7 khng3--loh8-khi3: ¡§Choan5 hau-siau5--e5!¡¨ Chheh-phaiN7-a2 phaiN7--leh, png7 ia